Na ọnwa nke isii, na afọ  2021, ọ sonyere na World Olympic Qualification Tournament nke emere na Paris, France na-enwe olileanya iru eru maka afọ 2020 Summer Olympics na Tokyo, Japan. N'ọnwa Ọktoba, na afọ 2021, o ritere ihe nrite ọlaọcha na ihe omume ya na afọ 2021 Mediterranean Karate Championships nke emere na Limassol, Saịprọs.
